(1451, 'gWchmsrK', 'The Solution', '', 1449, 1, 31, '2016-10-18 15:14:02', 31, '2016-10-18 15:14:02', '<p>Here you will need to make a summary of whatever was written in The Solution section. The prominent questions that need to be answered are<p><ul style=''color:#999;line-height: 2;''><li style=''list-style-type: lower-alpha;''>What is your solution to the customer''s problems and</li><li style=''list-style-type: lower-alpha;''>Why are your products or services so critically important for them?</li></ul></p>', 'The Solution', 1),
